    {
      "cell_type": "markdown",
      "source": "Piecewise function using `if`/`then`/`else`",
      "metadata": {}
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "source": "g(x) := if x >= 0 then sqrt(x) else -sqrt(-x);\n[g(4), g(-9)]",
      "metadata": {},
      "execution_count": null,
      "outputs": []
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "markdown",
      "source": "## Loops and Blocks\n\nUse `block()` for local variables and sequential statements.",
      "metadata": {}
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "source": "block([s: 0],\n  for i: 1 thru 100 do s: s + i,\n  s)",
      "metadata": {},
      "execution_count": null,
      "outputs": []
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "markdown",
      "source": "## List Operations",
      "metadata": {}
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "source": "makelist(i^2, i, 1, 10)",
      "metadata": {},
      "execution_count": null,
      "outputs": []
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "markdown",
      "source": "Map a function over a list",
      "metadata": {}
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "source": "map(lambda([x], x^3), [1, 2, 3, 4, 5])",
      "metadata": {},
      "execution_count": null,
      "outputs": []
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "markdown",
      "source": "Filter a list with `sublist()`",
      "metadata": {}
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "source": "sublist(makelist(i, i, 1, 20), primep)",
      "metadata": {},
      "execution_count": null,
      "outputs": []
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "markdown",
      "source": "Sum a list with `apply()`",
      "metadata": {}
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "source": "apply(\"+\", [1, 2, 3, 4, 5])",
      "metadata": {},
      "execution_count": null,
      "outputs": []
